description.narrative: New Element, which contributes to Health And Development In Early Childhood And Adolescence, Operations Support To Programme Delivery, Strengthening Primary Health Care And High-Impact Health Interventions. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building, Systems Strengthening To Leave No One Behind. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2021, pregnant women and new-borns, children and adolescents have equitable access to essential lifesaving health care services
